OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F426A1776881467
OL,3,CTwo arrests after report of sexual
OL,4,Cassault on 17-year-old soldier on army
OL,5,Cbase
OL,7,FAn investigation is underway after a
OL,8,Freport of a sexual assault on a 17-
OL,9,Fyear-old soldier at Catterick Garrison.
OL,11,FThe government's Defence Serious Crime
OL,12,FCommand (DSCC) confirmed on Tuesday
OL,13,F(21 April) that two members of the
OL,14,FArmed Forces have been arrested
OL,15,Ffollowing an investigation.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/4
