PN,42602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F426A1776881467
OL,3,CTwo arrests after report of sexual
OL,4,Cassault on 17-year-old soldier on army
OL,5,Cbase
OL,7,FIt is understood the ongoing inquiry
OL,8,Fcomes after the report of an alleged
OL,9,Fsexual assault last week on a 17-year-
OL,10,Fold boy, from Fife, believed to have
OL,11,Fbeen undertaking basic training at the
OL,12,FBritish Army's North Yorkshire base.
OL,14,FA DSCC spokesperson said: "Two members
OL,15,Fof the Armed Forces have been arrested
OL,16,Ffollowing an investigation by the
OL,17,FDefence Serious Crime Command.
OL,19,F"As the matter is subject to an
OL,20,Fongoing investigation, we will not
OL,21,Fcomment further."
OL,26,@}D@QO]
