OL,3,CTwo arrests after report of sexual
OL,4,Cassault on 17-year-old soldier on army
OL,5,Cbase
OL,7,FThe DSCC is the strategic command
OL,8,Fheadquarters for the Defence Serious
OL,9,FCrime Unit (DSCU) - an independent,
OL,10,Fprofessional, and global service
OL,11,Fpolice force.
OL,13,FAccording to the government website,
OL,14,Fthe force has jurisdiction to
OL,15,Finvestigate serious crime alleged to
OL,16,Fhave been committed by persons subject
OL,17,Fto service law, in the UK and overseas.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/4
